                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9606" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1448</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1464 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">餐饮界的一头倔“牛”--小放牛是如何出圈的？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A stubborn “cow” in the catering industry--How did Xiaofangniu become famous??</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王弘钰，张紫倩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北小放牛餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小放牛；两次定位；营销模式；管理策略；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xiaofangniu, Two positioning, Marketing mode, Management strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在餐饮行业逐渐饱和，市场竞争越来越激烈的背景下，在行业中生存已经成为各大餐饮企业亟需解决的问题。而河北小放牛餐饮管理有限公司（以下简称“小放牛”）却在众多餐饮企业中脱颖而出，在北京店面内每日客流量超1000人，并在各大餐饮榜上频频登榜，成功在餐饮界出圈，获得一席之地。本案例以小放牛的两次定位为出发点，重点描述了小放牛逆水行舟的营销模式以及优越的管理策略，旨在探究小放牛出圈背后的原因，以期能够给予其他餐饮企业一些借鉴和参考。但在消费者需求快速更迭与更追求创新性、多样性的时代，昙花一现的成功并不能带来长远的发展。案例最后引导学生探讨小放牛未来应如何根据市场需求的变化不断进行自身优化，在逆水行舟中牢牢把握手中的桨，倔得更久。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of gradually saturated catering industry and increasingly fierce market competition, survival in the industry has become an urgent problem that major catering enterprises need to solve. However, Hebei Xiaofangniu catering management Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as “Xiaofangniu”) stands out among many catering enterprises, with a daily customer flow of over 1000 people in its Beijing store, and frequently appearing on various dining rankings, successfully&#160;making a name for itself in the catering industry, earning its place among the top players. This case study takes the two positioning of Xiaofangniu as the starting point, focusing on the marketing model and superior management strategy of Xiaofangniu sailing against the current, aiming to explore the reasons behind Xiaofangniu’s popularity, in order to provide some reference and guidance for other catering enterprises. But in an era where consumer demand is rapidly changing and there is a greater pursuit of innovation and diversity, fleeting success cannot bring long-term development. At the end of the case, students are guided to explore how Xiaofangniu should continuously optimize itself according to changes in market demand in the future, firmly grasp the oars in its hand while sailing against the current, and be stubborn for longer.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销学》、《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP理论；品牌定位；4C营销理论；服务利润链理论；动态能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
